{"title":"UNPUBLISHED: Report a vehicle safety defect form","public_updated_at":"2013-04-29T09:17:00Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This form is used for reporting vehicle safety defects to <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr>. For more information about the safety defects scheme see ‘Consumers’ guide to vehicle safety defects’.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> has a specific team called the Vehicle Safety Branch (VSB) responsible for this work which adheres to the following codes of practice:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/code-of-practice-on-vehicle-safety-defects-and-recalls\">Code of practice on vehicle safety defects and recalls</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/code-of-practice-on-safety-defects-and-recalls-vehicle-aftermarket\">Code of practice on safety defects and recalls: vehicle aftermarket</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2013-04-29T10:17:00.000+01:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_494545\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/192694/Vehicle_Safety_Defect_Reporting_Form.doc\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/assets/pub-cover-doc-afe3b0a8a9511beeca890340170aee8b5649413f948e512c9b8ce432d8513d32.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a aria-describedby=\"attachment-494545-accessibility-help\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/192694/Vehicle_Safety_Defect_Reporting_Form.doc\">Report a vehicle safety defect form</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"references\">\n          Ref: <span class=\"unique_reference\">VOSA 22</span>\n        </span>\n        <span class=\"type\">MS Word Document</span>